document_data.DDEX2-01 - City of Danger:
{{main|City of Danger}}

{{Quote|''On the southern shores of the [[Moonsea]], the residents of [[Mulmaster]] have eked out a living where others would likely have given up long ago—in a bleak city where corruption is rampant and the [[Church of Bane]] holds sway. In these five short, introductory adventures, you will travel the breadth of the City of Danger, meet its people, see its sights, and witness firsthand how the city truly has earned its ominous moniker.''|}}

* '''Designer(s):''' [[Shawn Merwin]]
* '''Editor(s):''' [[Claire Hoffman]], [[Chris Tulach]], [[Travis Woodall]]
* '''Debut:''' March 12, 2015 (ConnCon)
* '''Released:''' April 1, 2015
* '''Levels:''' 1{{st}} – 2{{nd}}
* '''Setting:''' [[Mulmaster]]

document_data.DDEX2-02 - Embers of Elmwood:
{{main|Embers of Elmwood}}

{{Quote|''A derelict raft drifts into [[Mulmaster]]’s harbor carrying a young woman. Delirious with hunger, the only words she seems able to speak so far have been “ash and fire.” The only other clue to her identity is an ornate tattoo. Is the woman insane, or is something nefarious at play?''|}}

* '''Designer(s):''' [[Daniel Helmick]]
* '''Editor(s):''' [[Claire Hoffman]], [[Chris Tulach]], [[Travis Woodall]]
* '''Debut:''' March 13, 2015 (ConnCon)
