document_data.DDEX2-05 - Flames of Kythorn:
{{main|Flames of Kythorn}}

{{Quote|''During a summer drought, [[Mulmaster]] is threatened by a series of arson attacks. As the populace riots, accusations fly blaming [[Thayans]], residents of the ghettos, rowdy sailors, the refugees from [[Phlan]] and dozens of others. Can you solve the mystery before the city burns?''|}}

