document_data.DDEX2-14 - The Sword of Selfaril:
{{main|The Sword of Selfaril}}

{{Quote|''The fabled sword of Selfaril is told to bestow wisdom and power upon whomever wields it, so naturally its discovery has caused quite a stir in Mulmaster. All of this is complicated when a masked benefactor claims to not only know the truth about the blade, but also how it can be used to benefit the oppressed people of Mulmaster. Can it truly change Mulmaster for the better?''|}}

